data.description: Welcome to Pheobus! This residence boasts three spacious bedrooms, including an ensuite, along with two full bathrooms. Revel in the warmth of wood flooring throughout, complemented by modern gas appliances. The home also comes equipped with over 1,000 sq ft of unfinished basement space and eco-friendly solar panels. Conveniently situated near shops, restaurants, the HRBT, and more. This property invites you to infuse it with your unique style, creating a space that truly reflects your personal touch. Welcome home! The property was built prior to 1978 and lead based paint may potentially exist. This property may qualify for Seller Financing (Vendee). Make sure to ask about the 3D True Immersive Virtual Tour. This technology allows you to literally experience the home on any mobile device, laptop or desktop. You can measure rooms, view 3D dollhouse, view exterior, and interior and so much more. Check it out today! Some images have been edited by Artificial Intelligence.
